# Happy Boy Company Limited — Website Project Budget

> **Currency:** Ghana Cedis (GH₵)
> **Date Prepared:** 26 June 2026
> **Project:** Corporate Portfolio Website

---

## Project Scope

| Metric | Detail |
|---|---|
| Total Pages | **10** (Home, About, Collection, Farms, Homes, Nick Phones, Automobile, Oil & Gas, Mining, Contact) |
| Reusable Components | **9** (Navbar, Footer, HeroSlideshow, MarqueePortfolio, FadeIn, LazyVideo, LightboxGallery, BusinessCard, TikTokIcon) |
| Tech Stack | Next.js 16 · React 19 · TypeScript · Tailwind CSS 4 |
| Responsive | Fully responsive (Mobile, Tablet, Desktop) |

---

## 1. Frontend Development

| Item | Description | Cost (GH₵) |
|---|---|---|
| Project Setup & Architecture | Next.js 16 + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS 4 scaffold, routing, linting, folder structure | 1,500 |
| Home Page | Hero slideshow, marquee portfolio carousel, CTA section | 3,000 |
| About Page | Company story, leadership, mission/vision | 2,000 |
| Collection Page (Fashion) | Hero, philosophy section, 4-category grid with hover overlays, boutique CTA | 2,500 |
| Farms Page | Hero, philosophy + logo section, 4-item operations grid (images + videos), CTA | 2,500 |
| Homes Page (Real Estate) | Hero, property showcases, gallery | 2,500 |
| Nick Phones Page | Hero, 2-item lineup grid, iPhone/accessories showcase, CTA | 2,000 |
| Automobile Page | Hero, vehicle showcase, services section | 2,500 |
| Oil & Gas Page | "Coming Soon" placeholder with hero | 1,000 |
| Mining Page | Hero, operations philosophy, 4-item grid (images + videos), CTA | 2,500 |
| Contact Page | Contact form (international phone input), map, contact details | 2,500 |
| Navbar Component | Fixed floating nav, desktop dropdown (7 businesses), mobile hamburger with accordion, active-state highlighting | 2,500 |
| Footer Component | 4-column responsive layout, social links, business links, contact info | 1,500 |
| HeroSlideshow Component | Auto-cycling background image slideshow with crossfade transitions | 1,200 |
| MarqueePortfolio Component | Infinite-scroll horizontal marquee with business cards, hover-pause, "Coming Soon" badges | 2,000 |
| Animations & Interactions | FadeIn scroll reveals, lazy-loading videos, lightbox gallery, hover effects, micro-animations | 2,800 |
| Responsiveness & Cross-Browser Testing | Mobile + tablet optimization, Chrome/Safari/Firefox/Edge testing | 4,000 |
| SEO & Performance Optimization | Meta tags, image optimization, Lighthouse audit, code splitting | 3,500 |
| **Subtotal** | | **GH₵ 42,500** |

