## 2. Domain & Hosting (Year 1)

| Item | Description | Cost (GH₵) |
|---|---|---|
| Domain Registration | .com domain (1 year) | 250 |
| Hosting (Vercel Pro or VPS) | Production hosting with SSL, CDN, analytics (12 months) | 2,400 |
| Custom Email Setup | Professional email (e.g. info@happyboy.com) | 600 |
| CI/CD & Deployment | GitHub auto-deploy, DNS setup, SSL verification | 800 |
| **Subtotal** | | **GH₵ 4,050** |

